</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/ppySb7dUBpg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/29/sf-express-fake-message/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sf-express-fake-message</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>iWork 生產力 app 更新   Keynote + Pages + Numbers 全新功能</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Av76egZ3tvg/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[牙 Step]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Sep 2021 05:46:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[iwork]]></category><category><![CDATA[keynote]]></category><category><![CDATA[numbers]]></category><category><![CDATA[pages]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1063117</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日更新了 iWork 生產力 app，並為 Keynote、Pages 及 Numbers 帶來 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Apple </span>今日更新了<span class="s1"> iWork </span>生產力<span class="s1"> app</span>，並為 Keynote<span class="s1">、</span>Pages <span class="s1">及</span> Numbers 帶來新功能。<span class="s1">Keynote </span>讓演講者的相機畫面能夠直接顯示在簡報上，並提供多位演講者共同控制簡報；<span class="s1">Pages </span>在<span class="s1"> iPhone </span>上可以單直欄接續檢視文件，可隨時編輯；而 <span class="s1">Numbers 就</span>新增透視表功能。</p><p>首先在 Keynote 方面，用户現可選擇在<span class="s1"> iPhone</span>、<span class="s1">iPad </span>和<span class="s1"> Mac </span>上使用前置鏡頭，直接將<span class="s1"> live video </span>加入簡報中。演講者會出現在簡報內容的旁邊，<span class="s1">Live video </span>物件可以使用遮罩、邊線、陰影及倒影，並調整尺寸或款式。而 <span class="s1">Mac </span>用户可以連接多個外部相機，甚至可以將已連接的<span class="s1"> iPhone </span>或<span class="s1"> iPad </span>螢幕置入簡報當中 ，即時進行互動示範。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46-694x429.png" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46-694x429.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46-1280x791.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46-768x475.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46-1536x949.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.46.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17-694x425.png" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17-694x425.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17-1280x784.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17-768x470.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17-1536x941.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.29.17.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>另外，Keynote 新增多位演講者選項，<span class="s1"> iPhone</span>、<span class="s1">iPad </span>或<span class="s1"> Mac 用戶之間能夠自由切換去</span>控制共享的簡報。無論簡報是在同一個房間還是遠距離進行，所有演講者都可以輪流演示及切換下一張簡報。完成了自己的簡報內容後，用户可以將控制權交還主持人，或讓另一位共同演講者接手繼續小組簡報。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063121" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_multi-presenter_09282021.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在 Pages 方面，<span class="s1">配合</span> iPhone，<span class="s1">Screen View </span>會自動以單直欄接續顯示文字、圖像及其他內容。文字、相片及繪圖尺寸會調整去配合顯視器；表格亦可以水平橫掃。<span class="s1">Screen View </span>可用於所有文書處理文件，不需要任何額外設定。開啟<span class="s1"> Screen View </span>後，用户仍然可以完整地使用<span class="s1"> Pages </span>中的編輯工具。<span class="s1">Screen View </span>可以隨時關閉，用户在列印或發佈前，可隨時查看文件的頁面佈局。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.03-382x580.png" alt="" width="382" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.03-382x580.png 382w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.03-592x900.png 592w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.03-768x1167.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.03.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 382px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 開啟 <span class="s1">Screen View </span>前。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.46.23-392x580.png" alt="" width="392" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.46.23-392x580.png 392w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.46.23-608x900.png 608w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.46.23-768x1137.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.46.23.png 824w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 392px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.28-364x580.png" alt="" width="364" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.28-364x580.png 364w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.28-565x900.png 565w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-29-12.47.28.png 757w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 364px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 開啟 <span class="s1">Screen View 後</span>。</p><p>Numbers <span class="s1">推出透視表，可於</span> iPhone<span class="s1">、</span>iPad <span class="s1">及</span> Mac 上使用<span class="s1">。</span>用户可以將數據歸納、分類及重新排列。使用<span class="s1"> Numbers </span>製作透視表時，用户可以選取需要包含的數據、選擇如何分類數據，以及在側邊欄使用其他顯示選項。用户與他人分享透視數據時，源頭數據將得到保密；更可以從<span class="s1"> Microsoft Excel 滙出或</span>滙入透視表。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063125" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_pivot-tables_09282021.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 新的過濾條件功能可以讓用户在數據中找到重複的項目及獨特的數值，同時可以顯示或隱藏特定數值的橫列。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063126" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021-1125x900.jpg 1125w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021-768x614.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_radar_09282021.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Numbers 亦加入雷達圖表，相似數值會顯示為重疊區域，而相異及異常數值則更顯眼突出，讓用戶比較多個變數。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063127" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_translate_09282021-694x528.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="528" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_translate_09282021-694x528.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_translate_09282021-1182x900.jpg 1182w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_translate_09282021-768x585.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple_iWork-update_translate_09282021.jpg 1306w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 用户可以在 iWork app 中使用 iOS 15、iPadOS 15 及 macOS Monterey 的翻譯功能。</p><p class="p1">Keynote<span class="s1">、</span>Pages <span class="s1">及</span> Numbers <span class="s1">由今日起，用户可以在</span> App Store <span class="s1">及</span> Mac App Store <span class="s1">下載更新。</span><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2021/09/apple-unveils-new-features-in-iwork-suite-of-productivity-apps/">Apple</a><br />—<br />unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</p></p><div class="feedflare">
